==English==
=== Noun ===

([[Mach.]]) That which takes up or tightens; specifically, a device in a [[sewing]] machine for drawing up the slack thread as the needle
rises, in completing a [[stitch]].

=== Verb (transitive) ===

# to begin doing an activity on a regular basis
#: ''I've taken up knitting''
# to begin learning how to do something
#: ''I'm taking up piano lessons''
# to address an issue
#: ''Let's take this up with the manager''
# to bring something somewhere
#: ''Can you take this up to the front desk?''

=== Verb (intransitive) ===

# to resume
#: ''let's take up where we left off''

